title: Legend of William Tell 1998
description:
All 16 episodes of the New-Zealand tv-show, starring (among others) Kieren hutchinson

William Tell is on a quest to get the crystal arrow, so he can defeat Xax, the self-proclaimed 'Lord protector' of Kale.
With the help of his friends and a little magic, he might just succeed to put the princess Vara back on the throne. 

===========================================


Classic 1998 New Zealand TV Series.please seed and enjoy !
